###
# Test Posts API

### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts

### Get posts with pagination and search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts?search=&page=1&pageSize=5

### Get total count of posts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/count

### Get post by post ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/4

### Get posts by user ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/user/2

### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "Evening Yoga",
  "type": "Yoga",
  "date": "2026-04-13",
  "duration": "45",
  "intensity": "Medium",
  "picture": "https://example.com/yoga.jpg",
  "notes": "Relaxing session before bed."
}

### Update a post by post ID
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Updated: Felt even more relaxed!"
}

### Toggle like on a post — like post 1 as user 2
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/117/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1
}

### Toggle like again — unlike post 1 as user 2 (run twice to toggle off)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/1/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2
}

### Like post 1 as a different user (user 3)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/1/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3
}

### Delete a post by post ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/posts/5
